<template>
  <nav class="footer__display-tasks">
    <input class="footer__display-tasks--hide" type="radio" name="taskToDisplay" id="all" value="all" checked>
    <label class="footer__display-tasks--visible" for="all">All</label>
    <input class="footer__display-tasks--hide" type="radio" name="1" id="active" value="active">
    <label class="footer__display-tasks--visible" for="active">Active</label>
    <input class="footer__display-tasks--hide" type="radio" name="1" id="completed" value="completed">
    <label class="footer__display-tasks--visible" for="completed">Completed</label>
  </nav>
</template>
